<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The Zend_XmlRpc_Request_Http construct is missing the method and params arguments.  If you extend the Http class and then try to assign the method through the constructor, it doesn't get assigned to the internal _method property, though it does in Zend_XmlRpc_Request.</p>

    </div>
